<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Dozen" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Dozen,</orth> twelve in number: <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.93" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 93</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.566" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 566</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.4.193" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 4, 193</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 4.3.85" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. IV, 3, 85</bibl>. Followed by a subst. without <emph>of</emph>: <cit><quote>a d. years,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.279" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 279</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>thirty d. moons,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.167" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 2, 167</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.16" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 16</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 1.2.21" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. I, 2, 21</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 5.1.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado V, 1, 97</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.234" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 234</bibl>.  <bibl n="shak. shr 1.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. Ind. I, 27</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 3.4.173" default="NO" valid="yes">John III, 4, 173</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.4.387" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 4, 387</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.4.387" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 4, 387</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 3.2.102" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 102</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 3.2.102" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 102</bibl> <bibl n="shak. h8 1.4.105" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 4, 105</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 5.4.8" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 1.3.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 3, 24</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.4.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 4, 27</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 5.2.172" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 2, 172</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 1.2.41" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 2, 41</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.6.185" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 6, 185</bibl>. Followed by <emph>of</emph>: <cit><quote>seven d. of Scots,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.116" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 116</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.77" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 77</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.1.71" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B V, 1, 71</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.4.16" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 16</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.3.135" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 3, 135</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 4.6.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. IV, 6, 22</bibl>. <cit><quote>a d. of them:</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 4.5.110" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 5, 110</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. r2 5.2.97" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 V, 2, 97</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.183" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 183</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 3.6.88" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. III, 6, 88</bibl>. <cit><quote>knock them down by the --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 5.4.33" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 4, 33</bibl></cit>.
